<add><ab facs="#facs_10_line_1570516597100_242">wer </ab></add> <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_10_r1l1">gewalt hat </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Offıcıal </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l4">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vica<ex>r</ex>ıȷ</expan></del> ın geiſtlıchen ſachen </ab>
</del></div>
