<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l22">eŷden / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>Math<ex>eis</ex></expan> wenigheincʒ in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat hie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l23">geporen vnd auch von vater vnd von Muter ein rehts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l24">eekind ſeẏ / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ Jr dan <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden den </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough">die pfründe in ſant Maur Mauricien Capellen dem </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">Caplan die / dy <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von erbteils </del></ab>
