<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / dem Caplan / dem ſıe dıe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lıh<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
