<ab facs="#facs_10_r1l30">
<add>Alſo daʒ ir</add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd </del> den Caplan <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> ſıe die pfünde ın ſant <expan>Mauricʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
