</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_10" id="3v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Bischof czu Bamberg oder <add>wer</add>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>gewalt hat</add> in geistlichen sachen </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden vormals
                                    <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<add>und bey <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>M<ex>a</ex>rkart<ex>en</ex></expan> Waltman,
                                        <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener, empoten</add> haben
                            von Mertein Gewders und Matheis Wenigheinczen,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wegen, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> brief und auch des
                                    <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners, gewerbe darauf wol
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>und besunder</add>, daz ewr gnade <add>wissen wolle</add>, ob der
                                    <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Matheis Wenigheincz ein eekind
                            sey oder niht; also lassen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade wissen,
                            daz etlich <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>und frum</add> leut, <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, von <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                            Wenigheinczen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, wegen vor uns gewesen sein und
                                    <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns gesagt bey iren eyden, daz der
                                    <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>Math<ex>eis</ex></expan> Wenigheincz in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> stat hie geporen und auch von vater
                            und von muter ein rehts eekind sey. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                            caplan, dem die <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> die pfründe <add>hie</add> in sant
                            Mauricien capellen <add>von erbteils <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>lih<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                    <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan></add> die ir
                                <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>selig<ex>er</ex></expan> gedehtnüsse gestifft
